| **API/Router** | Request DTO | `Pydantic BaseModel` | `api/schemas/` | 接收 HTTP 请求、参数校验 |
| **API/Router** | Response DTO | `Pydantic BaseModel` | `api/schemas/` | 返回 HTTP 响应 |
| **Application** | Command / Query | `@dataclass` | `application/commands/` | 封装用例输入 |
| **Domain** | Entity | `@dataclass` | `domain/entities/` | 领域模型，承载业务逻辑 |
